                    <p class="text-dark-gray mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">Manage your entire product inventory. Add new items, update existing products, and remove discontinued items.</p>
                    <button 
                        onclick="navigateToProducts()"
                        class="w-full px-6 py-4 bg-off-black text-off-white rounded-xl hover:bg-dark-gray transition-colors font-semibold text-lg group-hover:scale-105 transform duration-300"
