                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-off-black mb-3 font-michroma">Order Management</h3>
                    <p class="text-dark-gray mb-6 font-medium leading-relaxed">View and manage all customer orders. Track order status, process refunds, and handle customer requests.</p>
                    <button 
                        onclick="navigateToOrders()"
